<section id="timeline" class="bg-gray-950 py-20 px-4 fade-in-up">
    <div class="max-w-screen-md mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-center text-white mb-10">Timeline Penting</h2>
        
        <div class="relative border-l border-gray-700 ml-4">                  
            <div class="mb-10 ml-8 relative">
                <span class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-blue-900 rounded-full -left-[46px] ring-8 ring-gray-950">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-300" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M20 4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1h-3V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H6V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2h20V4ZM0 18a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8H0v10Zm5-8h10a1 1 0 0 1 0 2H5a1 1 0 0 1 0-2Z"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <h3 class="flex items-center mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-white flex-wrap gap-2">
                    Coding Camp Registration
                    <span class="bg-blue-900 text-blue-300 text-xs font-medium px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded">OPEN</span>
                </h3>
                <time class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal text-gray-500">21 Okt 2025 – 31 Jan 2026</time>
                <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-400">Pendaftaran untuk mahasiswa, siswa, dan umum. Pastikan data lengkap.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mb-10 ml-8 relative">
                <span class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-gray-700 rounded-full -left-[46px] ring-8 ring-gray-950">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M20 4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1h-3V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H6V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2h20V4ZM0 18a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8H0v10Zm5-8h10a1 1 0 0 1 0 2H5a1 1 0 0 1 0-2Z"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Pengumuman (Coding Camp)</h3>
                <time class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal text-gray-500">6 Feb 2026</time>
                <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-400">Pengumuman seleksi administrasi & tes substansi.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-10 ml-8 relative">
                <span class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-purple-900 rounded-full -left-[46px] ring-8 ring-gray-950">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-300" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path d="M20 4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1h-3V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H6V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2h20V4ZM0 18a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8H0v10Zm5-8h10a1 1 0 0 1 0 2H5a1 1 0 0 1 0-2Z"/>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                <h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-white">METC Program</h3>
                <time class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal text-gray-500">Berkala / Bertahap</time>
                <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-400">
                    Jadwal kegiatan (Workshop, Hackathon, dll) akan diinformasikan secara berkala kepada pendaftar.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="mt-8 text-center text-xs text-gray-600">
            *Cek website resmi untuk perubahan jadwal.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
